title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table that is inside a grid cell
OB: Exporting data in a table that is inside a grid cell throws an exception
EB: Exporting data in a table that is inside a grid cell should not throw any exceptions
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a table into one grid cell. 2. Insert another table into another grid cell. 3. Export the data in the first table. 4. Check if any exceptions are thrown.
